Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.66,0:29:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.66,0:29:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you walk into this stunning gothic cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.03,0:29:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the most beautiful structures that man has ever made,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.51,0:29:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated in the 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.72,0:29:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And in today's world, they're all on their cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.72,0:29:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't believe our ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.70,0:29:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are in front of this breathtaking beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.55,0:29:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody, hello, I'm right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.27,0:29:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call Susan yet about the cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.52,0:29:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why they let them do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.58,0:29:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a certain umbrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.26,0:29:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.00,0:29:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the inspiration of the beautiful space, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.31,0:29:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But walking the labyrinth in Charnc Cathedral is 503.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.57,0:29:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Genuflexen, so all forms symbolic of, that are symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.18,0:30:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To do this in itself is 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.61,0:30:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So the charm of a country like Korea, which I have adored,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.18,0:30:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is everybody in Korea, every hotel, bellman, everybody greets you with Leslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.88,0:30:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very enchanting to live in a world in which everybody is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.61,0:30:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so it actually is a devotional act.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.35,0:30:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, that's ridiculous, turning prayer wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.29,0:30:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intention behind turning the prayer wheels that calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.25,0:30:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The burning of incense, when it's done devotionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.68,0:30:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything done devotionally is already 540 because of the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.49,0:30:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you're doing, even if it's playing jacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.97,0:30:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think playing jacks is a way of worshiping God,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it already calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the world, the province of faith and devotion, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a place for the skeptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.13,0:31:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the skeptic can only see the literal pedestrian image of a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.72,0:31:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't get the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.11,0:31:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of all these, the wailing wall, bathing in the Ganges,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.01,0:31:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the prayer of St. Francis of Assisi,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.27,0:31:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,bathing in the Ganges,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.16,0:31:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ganges, 540, you know, bathing in the Ganges.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.81,0:31:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River, let's calibrate the Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.18,0:31:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River, we have permission to calibrate that here, is over 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.79,0:31:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The dirtiest, yuckiest river in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.52,0:31:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The garbage of 30, 40 cities dumps into the Ganges.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.91,0:31:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead bodies go bumping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.27,0:31:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it calibrates that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it calibrate higher than most of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.50,0:31:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The places?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.98,0:31:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, when it's full of garbage and dead floating bodies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.46,0:31:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember being in China and, forget with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.00,0:31:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the Yellow River, the Yangtze River, I think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.08,0:32:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was in the bottom of the ship and I can hear this boom, boom,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.50,0:32:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,against the bulkhead, boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.04,0:32:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I go up around, look over the side, it's just a dead body bumping against, boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.13,0:32:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of feces, dead body, dead dog, garbage, floating down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.16,0:32:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can a river calibrate at 540?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.74,0:32:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of its sanctification over the many centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.55,0:32:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ganges River itself is indeed a holy river.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.57,0:32:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the linear secularist would say it's full of garbage and disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.58,0:32:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But thousands and thousands for centuries after centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.26,0:32:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,have sanctified the Ganges River and the Ganges is truly a holy river.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.41,0:32:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I thought that's quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.75,0:32:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't suggest drinking any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.74,0:33:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.04,0:33:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I never drank any of it, although I did swallow some water in the Yangtze
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.13,0:33:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,or someplace like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.21,0:33:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another place I discovered, I experienced a miracle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.47,0:33:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost got killed in the miraculous curve and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.77,0:33:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being squashed to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.16,0:33:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dropped by this heavy current, swept off this buoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.61,0:33:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,my body almost snapped in half with a steel cable
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.53,0:33:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that shot across the top of the buoy, almost cut my head off,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I fell into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.46,0:33:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And in between these ships, they were smashing against each other
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.03,0:33:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hit it right for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.74,0:33:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My body just went like this up on the prow of one of the ships
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.48,0:33:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and there I was, six inches this way, you're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.72,0:33:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,six inches this way, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the current took me right there to the prow of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.98,0:33:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.51,0:33:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,People say that's accidental, oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.23,0:34:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation and meditation then.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.78,0:34:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one's consciousness evolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.03,0:34:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is first you are focusing on form, it's registering,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.28,0:34:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to recognize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.03,0:34:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because there is a watcher experience going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.07,0:34:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can withdraw in your meditation and your contemplation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.05,0:34:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's relatively quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.75,0:34:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to tell people,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.09,0:34:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,things that are relatively quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.78,0:34:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By intention, you can begin to realize there's no person going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.63,0:34:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's a vanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.59,0:34:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that what's going on is observing and witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.94,0:34:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't take any great area of addition,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.32,0:34:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual area of addition,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.96,0:34:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in any kind of contemplation or meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.36,0:34:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to withdraw from thinking I am that,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.40,0:34:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to realizing that how do I know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.84,0:34:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of witnessing, observing,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.34,0:35:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is witnessing and observing something there is a you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.21,0:35:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.51,0:35:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a you doing it, you could stop it, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.32,0:35:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't stop witnessing and observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.11,0:35:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody in this room right now is witnessing and observing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomena of this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.07,0:35:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want you to observe and be aware that it's happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.63,0:35:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening spontaneously, autonomously, as a consequence of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.48,0:35:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.53,0:35:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing, observing is not something you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.88,0:35:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but then the you witnessing or observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.38,0:35:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing and observing is happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.57,0:35:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think, shall I witness and observe
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience what's happening today?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to realize that instead of a personal you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.15,0:36:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's a phenomena occurring,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.23,0:36:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just like vision, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.92,0:36:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no I that is seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.67,0:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Vision is seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.67,0:36:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.17,0:36:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can draw back from identifying with the content of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.21,0:36:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and become aware that observing and witnessing is going on of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.42,0:36:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's then not too big a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.42,0:36:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize that observing and witnessing is an autonomous, spontaneous,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.42,0:36:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomenon,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no personal you doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.32,0:36:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what is observing and witnessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.82,0:36:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The next step is,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.82,0:36:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's obvious that it's consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.07,0:36:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization that I am not the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.76,0:37:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the observer-witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.26,0:37:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not the observer-witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.26,0:37:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that you're the observer-witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.76,0:37:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you even know you're observing or witnessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.76,0:37:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of the light of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.76,0:37:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You get closer and closer to the Self,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.46,0:37:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the capital S, Self,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.15,0:37:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that the phenomena is happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.90,0:37:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.40,0:37:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no person speaking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.94,0:37:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The speakingness is happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.13,0:37:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an autonomous, spontaneous emergence of the potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.63,0:37:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the purusha, the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.21,0:37:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the non-personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.21,0:37:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no expectation of what it's going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.09,0:37:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no expectation of what it's going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.59,0:37:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what it's going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.09,0:37:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.78,0:37:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it at the same time you hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.46,0:37:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.46,0:37:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.80,0:37:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.80,0:38:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's happening spontaneously and autonomously of its own,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.51,0:38:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that has different karmic implications, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.50,0:38:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the light of consciousness radiating forth as your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.69,0:38:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that you exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.88,0:38:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that below consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.88,0:38:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the entity is not aware that it exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.38,0:38:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists, but it does not know that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.80,0:38:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not know that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.84,0:38:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, but it does not know that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.17,0:38:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only over 200 that you know that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.78,0:38:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to a crowd like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.28,0:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that would sound ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.86,0:38:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the people on the planet are,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.86,0:38:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but frankly do not experience
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.36,0:38:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.71,0:39:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this, they have no concern for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.34,0:39:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What characterizes level from 200 up,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.21,0:39:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you project onto the others the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.21,0:39:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're aware of in yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.21,0:39:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that you exist and therefore their value is the same as yours
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.21,0:39:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the same premise that they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.67,0:39:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, although they see people,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.19,0:39:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they are not aware that they exist as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.42,0:39:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, other people have no value.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.84,0:39:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To a dictator who calibrates,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.84,0:39:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all the world's dictators calibrated 90,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.84,0:39:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,both in the past and currently,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.84,0:39:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,some even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.59,0:39:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't even cause a twinge
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.76,0:39:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill 300,000 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.03,0:39:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even cause a twinge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.09,0:39:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.82,0:40:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said is so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.26,0:40:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that shocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.26,0:40:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so shocking, that's why America can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.26,0:40:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the citizens can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.73,0:40:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.80,0:40:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you could kill 300,000 people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.30,0:40:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or half a million or,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.80,0:40:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and Chairman Mill's starving China,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.61,0:40:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million and not feel a twinge about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.53,0:40:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you kill 10 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.53,0:40:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and not even feel anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.17,0:40:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the implications of that are profound,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.73,0:40:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The expectation, the restraint,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.73,0:40:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that the enemy will be restrained by common decency
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.21,0:40:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is a laughable absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.21,0:40:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no common decency
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.21,0:41:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,by which they will be restrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.23,0:41:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.73,0:41:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because below 200, although you exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't really experience your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.73,0:41:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You live a life like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.23,0:41:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal is, but it does not know that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.98,0:41:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ask my cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.32,0:41:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are you a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.00,0:41:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat says, what does that mean to be a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.94,0:41:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, well, I'll read it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.94,0:41:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get down the encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.48,0:41:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.01,0:41:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I flip through it, I read to the kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.01,0:41:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,what it means to be a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.55,0:41:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, that's interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.55,0:41:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.30,0:41:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.59,0:41:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, I'm not any of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.09,0:41:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, well, then who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.09,0:41:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitty says, I'm just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.92,0:42:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.30,0:42:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness then stops identifying
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.92,0:42:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the content of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.92,0:42:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.30,0:42:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It transcends any illusions of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.34,0:42:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to experience and witness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.46,0:42:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that all things are happening
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.46,0:42:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,autonomously of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.55,0:42:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That creation is an ongoing unfoldment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.59,0:42:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of thinking in terms of causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.59,0:42:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,see that all things are unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.59,0:42:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.01,0:42:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of emergence,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.01,0:42:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,not a causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.36,0:42:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are happening as a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.36,0:42:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of emergence, not causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.36,0:43:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make a big jump in spiritual advancement
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.36,0:43:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you begin to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.38,0:43:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are happening because
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.38,0:43:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that is their potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.38,0:43:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If the surrounding field is adequate
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.38,0:43:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the conditions are appropriate,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.38,0:43:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it will...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.13,0:43:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So as from consciousness levels 540 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.48,0:43:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous becomes almost continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.63,0:43:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At 570, the unfolding of everything is miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.63,0:43:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.73,0:43:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're witnessing is the miracle of creation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.73,0:43:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as it unfolds in one detail after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.73,0:43:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, there's no parking place there
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.73,0:43:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of the opera house.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.38,0:43:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lincoln Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.01,0:43:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you leave from home and you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.13,0:43:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right next to Lincoln Center,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.13,0:43:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the very best, super best parking space available.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.13,0:43:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring your car up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.13,0:44:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The car moves out and you pull in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.13,0:44:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's like, yeah, it's always that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.65,0:44:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.71,0:44:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a continuous unfoldment of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.01,0:44:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize that all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.01,0:44:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is the miracle of creation itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.51,0:44:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation is continuous and unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.69,0:44:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To the lower mind, it looks like causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.59,0:44:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To the higher mind, it realizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.59,0:44:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an infinite number of potentialities.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.59,0:44:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And which one will manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.59,0:44:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.44,0:44:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.40,0:44:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I wasn't thinking of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.76,0:44:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.75,0:44:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It just suddenly goes nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.21,0:44:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.71,0:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All is spontaneously emergent.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.76,0:45:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There is that emergence, that potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.76,0:45:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To try to be, that's what you're trying to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.76,0:45:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.69,0:45:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.51,0:45:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the cat, we are it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.38,0:45:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why search for that which you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.59,0:45:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty, why should I search for being a cat when I am a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.53,0:45:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of all the headaches, that saves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.75,0:45:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.25,0:45:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.61,0:45:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Three minutes to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.53,0:45:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, where did the morning go?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.53,0:45:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody has stolen the morning. Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.38,0:46:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody has stolen the morning? Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.36,0:46:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.86,0:46:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The implications are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.07,0:46:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If seriousness, if you can take being serious seriously, it's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.57,0:46:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's comical, being serious is comical, like everything else is comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.57,0:46:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The impact, the impact for the everyday reality of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.07,0:46:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is that consciousness level below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.09,0:46:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,has a different brain physiology than 200 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.13,0:46:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the sophistry and the do-gooderism isn't going to change this basic fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.01,0:46:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 people are run by the animal instinctual
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.55,0:46:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and from 200 and up, it's the first time that the spiritual energy, Kundalini energy, comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.92,0:46:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini energy begins to flow around.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.42,0:46:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.92,0:46:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens is it shifts the brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.25,0:47:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 is being run by animal instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.59,0:47:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of society today and throughout history is animal instinct, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.59,0:47:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know if you're talking about a country or a wolf pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.59,0:47:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to invade the country next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.82,0:47:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what wolf packs do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.82,0:47:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The dominant male has to, you know, got to have the dominant alpha male.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.82,0:47:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is he invading the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.82,0:47:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Invading the country next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.32,0:47:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he wants, because he's always wanting power and space
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.32,0:47:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore he is just an animal, is he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.98,0:47:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing more than an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.98,0:47:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a furless animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.98,0:47:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have fur, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.75,0:47:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the animal without fur?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.75,0:47:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine getting yourself born on this planet without fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.75,0:47:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if that isn't dumb at the beginning of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.07,0:47:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, the input, you see something out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.07,0:48:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a fast, fast relay to the thalamus.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.11,0:48:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And very fast to the emotional center of the amygdala.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.88,0:48:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And very slowly does it go through the prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.26,0:48:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person says, screw you, goddammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.63,0:48:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then his cortex says, murder is against the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.63,0:48:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.86,0:48:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're capable of murder, you're also capable of lying, so you just make up a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.36,0:48:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory of this event is stored in your hippocampus.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.98,0:48:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.48,0:48:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the animal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.48,0:48:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's consciousness level below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.48,0:48:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man's history, the reason he's been at war almost constantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.73,0:48:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is because he is an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.86,0:48:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The prefrontal torque, what does the prefrontal cortex do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.30,0:49:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.80,0:49:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He learns to be a clever animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.55,0:49:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting you with fangs and teeth, he gets an atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.90,0:49:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets dynamite, roadside bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.40,0:49:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the prefrontal cortex intelligence is now put at the service of the animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.90,0:49:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a dangerous animal before, you got a really dangerous animal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.44,0:49:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You give a dangerous animal, calibrates at 190, or 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.92,0:49:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these world dictators playing around with atomic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.21,0:49:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.55,0:49:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He calibrates at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.55,0:49:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how he thinks, this is how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.05,0:49:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you give him atomic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.55,0:49:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have an animal that lives by the tooth and the nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.05,0:49:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you give him atomic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.55,0:49:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prefrontal cortex now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.55,0:49:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you learn to be a smarter animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.55,0:49:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Above level 200, you see the brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.07,0:50:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So below 200, left brain dominance, linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.57,0:50:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Releases adrenaline, alarm, resistance, thymus stress, disrupts the acupuncture meridian,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.80,0:50:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to diseases, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.30,0:50:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapped to emotions twice as fast as through the brain prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.13,0:50:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At level 200, the etheric energy starts to rise and you shift from left brain to right brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.34,0:50:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the input is fast to the cerebral cortex and importantly to the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.76,0:50:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.76,0:50:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So above right brain dominance is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.76,0:50:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It puts forth endorphins instead of adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.26,0:50:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.76,0:50:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It supports the thymus gland.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.76,0:50:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Increases immunity and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.76,0:50:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Balances the acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.26,0:50:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get a positive kinesiologic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.98,0:50:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.48,0:50:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 and above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.21,0:51:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And to not know the difference will cost you your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.71,0:51:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't know the difference in the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.00,0:51:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 200 then, and the last thing that we want to say and then we'll break for lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.00,0:51:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is as the kundalini energy rises,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.00,0:51:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.09,0:51:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the formation of the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.09,0:51:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.69,0:51:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the etheric brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.69,0:51:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain is an energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.69,0:51:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy field which doesn't happen until you get to level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.69,0:51:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, everybody has a group etheric energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.69,0:51:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An attractor field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.69,0:51:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All animals below 200 do not have individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.69,0:51:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.59,0:51:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.09,0:51:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and up, you now have an etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.09,0:51:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You have individual personal karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.01,0:51:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain then is an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.94,0:52:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people here have been out of body?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.53,0:52:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.53,0:52:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when you're out of body, you think just as well as when you're in body.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.03,0:52:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.98,0:52:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the etheric brain is energy and not physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.48,0:52:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does thinking this come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.63,0:52:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.63,0:52:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes about, the energy field of the etheric brain by induction activates the neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.86,0:52:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The neurons in that physical brain are activated by induction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.86,0:52:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like magnetism induces electricity in a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.96,0:52:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by cause, but by induction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the field, spiritual intention and commitment then, activates the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.34,0:52:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini begins to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.88,0:52:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You see and experience the world differently than people do below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.94,0:52:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, how can so-and-so think that or do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.73,0:53:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because that is how the world is experienced and how it looks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.96,0:53:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they kill innocent people?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.46,0:53:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the way it looks to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.96,0:53:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What to you would be abhorrent but abhorrent to them is appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.57,0:53:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, golly, that's enough to think about for quite a few years, coming to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.57,0:53:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get all that digested before lunch, it's going to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.07,0:53:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to convene again at what time?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.07,0:53:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.55,0:53:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to convene again at two o'clock, California time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.17,0:53:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to say to them, it's so little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.67,0:53:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have quite a few people that have come from out of the country to see us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.86,0:54:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could stand up so we could acknowledge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.86,0:54:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you are from Ethiopia, Scotland, England.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.11,0:54:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you so much for coming such a long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.19,0:54:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,John, are you hearing Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.19,0:54:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.69,0:54:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to talk a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.19,0:54:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I said enough this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.19,0:54:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.21,0:54:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm obsessive compulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.21,0:54:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to feel satisfied that I've said all the things that are important to have said.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.21,0:54:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a wallop of books here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.94,0:54:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Shen writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.57,0:54:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.82,0:54:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brand new pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.28,0:54:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.67,0:54:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that writing? Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.32,0:55:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.07,0:55:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.57,0:55:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.48,0:55:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in Excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.15,0:55:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is really short, so I would like to make a quick announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.15,0:55:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've started a grassroots website for people who are dedicated to enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.15,0:55:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and facilitated by your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.65,0:55:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called VeritasNetwork.com.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.94,0:55:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All the services will always be free to the students who log on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.44,0:55:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.44,0:55:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, in 12-step programs, they have the idea of a sponsorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.82,0:55:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.82,0:55:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have selected you as my teacher, or it was selected for me for you to be my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.38,0:55:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have your sponsorship and your blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.17,0:56:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to be his sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.73,0:56:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be his sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.73,0:56:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no vice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.11,0:56:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no, well, at least that I can speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.11,0:56:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that I can speak of publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.78,0:56:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But throughout all my future obstacles, will you sponsor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.78,0:56:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The work itself sponsors you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.78,0:56:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of the work sponsors you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.78,0:56:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a personal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.88,0:56:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You need the truth of the teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.38,0:56:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.88,0:56:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The sponsor is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.26,0:56:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.38,0:56:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.34,0:56:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.73,0:56:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they say about telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.28,0:57:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've told the truth, quickly leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.65,0:57:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave town?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.65,0:57:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.17,0:57:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the blogs we get are like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.17,0:57:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.17,0:57:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.55,0:57:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about practice
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.05,0:57:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and where I could use a little more insightful guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.55,0:57:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.55,0:57:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.55,0:57:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When you talk about the fourth state and being in the,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.55,0:57:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,being the silent background.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.55,0:57:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave him just a little bit because he's having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.05,0:57:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I start off?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.55,0:57:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.05,0:57:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.05,0:57:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.05,0:57:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is about practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.05,0:57:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.05,0:57:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.55,0:57:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.05,0:57:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My personal practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.05,0:57:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.55,0:57:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When you talk about the fourth state and being in the silent background
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.05,0:57:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then about being,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.55,0:57:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,holding something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.90,0:58:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hold something in my mind, it gets a little noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.40,0:58:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when that's, that silent background that you talk about being,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.98,0:58:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it when I'm meditating.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.98,0:58:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it when I'm with a group that I work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.48,0:58:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my, when I'm out in places where I'm caught up in habitual distractions,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.48,0:58:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.48,0:58:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what's a good way to practice that, trying to be that silent background?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.63,0:58:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with intentional set.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.96,0:58:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when you make a declaration, a spiritual declaration,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.23,0:58:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that is an, it's called an attentional set.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.78,0:58:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a psychiatrist named, PhD, a research psychiatrist named Medina,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.28,0:58:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,M-E-D-I-N-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.28,0:59:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just written three recent articles that appeared in Psychiatric News.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.28,0:59:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on attentional set.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.28,0:59:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That your intention sets priorities
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.01,0:59:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's cascades of dominance within the neurologic system.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.15,0:59:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've set the priorities by your declaration of your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.15,0:59:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intention is what dominates your choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.15,0:59:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings up the question of free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.15,0:59:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it such a thing as a free will?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.65,0:59:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, within a certain intentional set, you have alternate choices available.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.15,0:59:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.05,0:59:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of it is spiritual practice and discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.05,0:59:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, how to not get entrapped by the world with every squeak and moan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.05,0:59:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.28,0:59:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.01,1:00:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intention will take care of those times if you stay with your own devotion?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.48,1:00:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The attentional set means that you have made a decision to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.98,1:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you make a decision to be that way, when it varies,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.42,1:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes to your attention because that's outside your set.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.42,1:00:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.48,1:00:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.46,1:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Attentional set.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.46,1:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.48,1:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Medina, M-E-D-I-N-A.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.80,1:00:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.30,1:00:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wrote a series of three articles on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.30,1:00:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.80,1:00:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Neurologic correlation is what they teach.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.30,1:00:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.80,1:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.80,1:00:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an announcement.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.80,1:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They said I could make an announcement before I ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.30,1:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I may please do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.80,1:01:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Some folks and I are starting a David Hawkins study group in Santa Monica in January
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.92,1:01:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're planning on meeting once a month on a Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.92,1:01:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So if anybody is interested in being a part of that, please send me an email.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.92,1:01:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can email me at telly at earthlink.net
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.42,1:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the trick is to spell telly correctly which is T like Tom, E-L-Y, T-E-L-Y at earthlink.net.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.92,1:01:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.69,1:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about how...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.19,1:01:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks one of those foreign languages.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.40,1:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-W net talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.69,1:01:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got an A like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.98,1:01:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-W and then there's all kinds of little things.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.19,1:01:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you end up making a mistake in one of the little things, you end up in a totally different universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.69,1:01:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're acquainted with that world.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.21,1:02:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and tell me what you're going to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.21,1:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.21,1:02:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you going to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.21,1:02:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.21,1:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how to reconcile two seemingly opposite truths.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.21,1:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, there's the idea that you can create your own reality by thinking...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.21,1:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.21,1:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.21,1:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.21,1:02:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get that from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.21,1:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what I've gotten from you is more the idea of attractor fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.21,1:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.21,1:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And which seems to me to be similar to...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.21,1:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar to the idea that you can create your own reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.21,1:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't say anything about creating your own reality, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.71,1:02:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.84,1:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.84,1:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess I'm confused because...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.34,1:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that from somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.48,1:02:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got what I thought was some of that from you...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.48,1:02:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.48,1:02:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.67,1:02:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.67,1:02:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The creating of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.67,1:02:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To create your own reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.67,1:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.67,1:02:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what I think I've gotten from you is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.67,1:02:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is the you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.67,1:02:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does it mean to create?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.67,1:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do they mean by reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.67,1:02:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.67,1:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.67,1:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very confusing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.67,1:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a whole symposium all day on it because it doesn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.67,1:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can spend all day playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.67,1:03:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What I think I've gotten from you is that what you hold in your thoughts will then manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.67,1:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.67,1:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.67,1:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the higher your level of consciousness, the more that is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.67,1:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.67,1:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.67,1:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The more...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.67,1:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher the level of consciousness, what you hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.67,1:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I teach you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.67,1:03:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.67,1:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But so then there's no...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.67,1:03:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing about then willing something?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.67,1:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Creating something by...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.67,1:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you wouldn't agree with the idea that you create your own reality, basically?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.67,1:03:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.86,1:03:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're enamored with that slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.86,1:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.86,1:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew what it...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.86,1:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was a truth, you wouldn't be asking me, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.86,1:03:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.86,1:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how to reconcile that with the ideas of...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.86,1:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.86,1:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.86,1:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.88,1:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.88,1:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that that's not a true thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.88,1:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.88,1:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the answer to non-sense?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.88,1:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.88,1:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.88,1:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.88,1:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.88,1:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.88,1:03:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.88,1:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.88,1:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.88,1:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.84,1:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.84,1:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that that's not a true thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.84,1:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.84,1:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the answer to non-sense?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.76,1:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.21,1:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.63,1:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying really hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.63,1:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what she's trying to get sense out of something, but it's one of those redundancies.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.63,1:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a redundancy, you can't get out of the puzzle box.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.88,1:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the box that says, everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.88,1:04:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.88,1:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,slip of paper and says, everything in this box
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.98,1:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is false. You put it in the box and close
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.01,1:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.61,1:04:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A double
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.21,1:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,negative does not create a positive, so
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.17,1:04:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot get the answer to
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.69,1:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,conundrums, you know? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.88,1:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two years since I saw you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.84,1:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,last, and what
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.76,1:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,happened since then is the nothingness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.82,1:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is available, looking inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.71,1:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothingness is there, but
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.71,1:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that this is
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.82,1:05:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,just another block, and that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.76,1:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,allness is available.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.90,1:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How to change from nothingness to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.90,1:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,allness. What says
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.44,1:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's nothing? Looking
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.96,1:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,inside, there is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.40,1:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.38,1:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something. There's something saying that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.42,1:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing. Right. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.21,1:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer. What is saying
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.34,1:05:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's nothing? You're not saying there's
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.36,1:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. You're negating what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.76,1:05:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. There's a something
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.19,1:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,saying there's nothing. Right. That's the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.15,1:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway out. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.19,1:05:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is reality. There's nothing to say
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.69,1:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's nothing in reality. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.23,1:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.71,1:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.92,1:05:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.90,1:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.28,1:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen both of you in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.23,1:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.11,1:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These conundrums, and they become
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.46,1:06:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,memes, M-E-M-E,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.69,1:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and they become
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.76,1:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of new age spirits of jargon,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.59,1:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody puzzles them,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.03,1:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have endless symposiums and all that kind of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.96,1:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,stuff, and it's going around
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.03,1:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and around about
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.40,1:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,hypotheses and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.51,1:06:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.26,1:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.11,1:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak in your writings about when the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.55,1:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to slow down, that there is a progression
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.71,1:06:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from perception to vision, to seeing essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.15,1:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And my experience has been that when I look at
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.76,1:06:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,something natural, I begin to see, for example,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.55,1:06:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if I look at a tree, I see a certain amount of space
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.78,1:06:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,holding it up, a kind of suspension, a kind of,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.03,1:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,more of an emerging of space, and a receding of form.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.67,1:06:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the kind of experience that happens as the mind begins to slow down?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.75,1:06:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's transitional, yeah, transitional.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.75,1:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the exquisite beauty and perfection of it, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.23,1:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning the mind says, look, that's a crooked tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.23,1:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should chop it down, it's not standing straight,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.23,1:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,all trees are supposed to stand straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.23,1:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while you see that it is expressing something else,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.23,1:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it's a perfect crooked tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.23,1:07:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there sort of a presentation by space?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.23,1:07:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's almost like space is presenting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.07,1:07:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The object, does that kind of make any sense?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.07,1:07:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the essence of its reality shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.07,1:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the perfection of all things.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.07,1:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that this tree like this is equally as perfect as this,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.13,1:07:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they aesthetically fit a different,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.13,1:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,presumptive aesthetic pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.13,1:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.46,1:07:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People are always wanting to chop down crooked trees.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.46,1:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they take away all my beautiful crooked old trees,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.46,1:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave nothing but the straight ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.92,1:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight trees are okay too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.92,1:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.19,1:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I talk while you write?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.71,1:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.71,1:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm very happy to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.71,1:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I come.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.71,1:08:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say unlimited, no, unlimited thank you for staying in this form,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.98,1:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.98,1:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying in this form so she can talk to, so you can talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.97,1:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you very much for staying in this form.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.97,1:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that form, there, you're talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.97,1:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, that form.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.97,1:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.19,1:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, that's the only one I can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.19,1:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's forms every place around the whole room today.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.19,1:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do with them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.19,1:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.19,1:08:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was told that there's only one question,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.19,1:08:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have many questions,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.19,1:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought maybe you can decide which one would be more beneficial to answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.52,1:08:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, keep it down to 30 questions, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.61,1:08:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so this, one of them is related to oneness,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.61,1:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is what exactly it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.61,1:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure, more I read, more I feel like I don't understand things.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.64,1:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so oneness is one I would like to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.64,1:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other one, it seems that I, maybe I misunderstood,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.64,1:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but all of the book I read is it seems that you need to have someone
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.64,1:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that is already enlightened beside you in order to achieve enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.64,1:09:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And obviously, as I'm here with you right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.64,1:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but usually that's, I'm not living here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.64,1:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do I do if that's true?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.64,1:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So choose whatever question you think is more beneficial to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.13,1:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to have a living teacher in your proximity.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.22,1:09:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need is the energy field or of a teacher who is enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.22,1:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That then goes with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.22,1:09:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can then forget about the teacher if you wish, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.22,1:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because the energy field is all you need to pick up the information.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.22,1:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not understandable without certain energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.22,1:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We sort of explained that this morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.22,1:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that as the Kundalini energy rises,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.22,1:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the etheric brain consciousness becomes more advanced.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.68,1:10:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which was not comprehensible at one level suddenly becomes an aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.68,1:10:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see it by revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.68,1:10:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often when you're not even thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.25,1:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just walking along and all of a sudden you've got,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.25,1:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, I've got what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.34,1:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.34,1:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.15,1:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can mull it over, meditate on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.15,1:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.15,1:10:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,let it be on its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.73,1:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.52,1:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.57,1:10:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.61,1:10:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love your team that's behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.61,1:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel their support.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.61,1:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel their love.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.61,1:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're like rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.39,1:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the rock Selena.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.64,1:11:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.13,1:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This lady just asked my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.13,1:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I, years ago, a couple years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.19,1:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you and I sat across from you in Sedona and I held your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.19,1:11:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And prior to that,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.19,1:11:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I had listened to maybe a couple of hundred hours of you speaking on audio.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.19,1:11:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.19,1:11:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it seemed like I didn't mean hardly anything until I sat across from you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.19,1:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I held your hand and you looked into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.19,1:11:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And now when I listen to you on cassette or see your DVDs,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.19,1:11:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can bring that context instantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.19,1:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.02,1:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.02,1:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And why, I guess you answered it with that last lady,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.43,1:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but is it the same thing in visiting a relic or holy places
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.43,1:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that you get the context of a place?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.78,1:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.23,1:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's a frequency that transmits down through the ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.23,1:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's through the etheric brain, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.23,1:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,through the higher chakras.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.56,1:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The chakras above the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.63,1:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more, the Buddhic bodies, the Christ body,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.63,1:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the Atmic body, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.63,1:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And the frequency of the energy field vibrates down through the ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.01,1:12:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it goes from one to the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.01,1:12:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We all transmit it to each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.01,1:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, of course, when we combine like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.01,1:12:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we all share it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.10,1:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we all sort of come on the planet together
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.10,1:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and go off the planet together, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.10,1:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 50 years in between individuals,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.35,1:12:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but, you know, in time, that's like the same minute, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.35,1:12:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred years is like a second in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.35,1:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you take about 10 seconds and just Aum with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.35,1:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aum.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.52,1:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just first want to thank you for being here today
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.59,1:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and sharing your just incredibly radiant presence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.68,1:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with all of us here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.31,1:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Wally and Cathy, the springboard's to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.60,1:13:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thank them, too, wherever they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.00,1:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess we're running into a familiar theme here,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.00,1:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but my question also has to do with proximity
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.00,1:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.00,1:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you in person three times now,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.00,1:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get more benefit coming up here on stage
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.00,1:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and being this close to you and looking you in the eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.00,1:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,than I do sitting in the audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.00,1:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get more out sitting in the audience
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.00,1:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,than I do sitting at home reading your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.00,1:14:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just wondering if it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.13,1:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't take disciples,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.13,1:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but is it possible to find somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.13,1:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,like Ramana Maharshi used to do
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.13,1:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,who takes disciples and to sit at the feet
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.13,1:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of an enlightened master such as yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.13,1:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for three years or...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.13,1:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're saying it's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.13,1:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.13,1:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you pick up the energy frequency
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.13,1:14:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher who got it elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.13,1:14:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,comes down through him to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.13,1:14:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you dedicate to studying and meditating on the work.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.55,1:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the teacher periodically if that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.64,1:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that starts a process going,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.64,1:14:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the process takes over.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.64,1:14:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You initiated a process,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.64,1:14:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the process then takes over.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.25,1:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, because you're being drawn by the future
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.25,1:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of propelled by the past,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.25,1:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so if your destiny is enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.25,1:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that means that destination is pulling you in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.25,1:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're certainly pulling me in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.25,1:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of your intention to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.25,1:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it would have no appeal to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.25,1:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.72,1:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your decision that gives it the power it has.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.89,1:15:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.89,1:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher tells me that I should not have any goal,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.52,1:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have such a strong goal for to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.52,1:15:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teacher tells you you should not have any goals?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.52,1:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I should not have goals or desires.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.52,1:15:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.84,1:15:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So your goal is to not have goals, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.84,1:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that is about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.03,1:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my meditation, I'm wondering what that process.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.03,1:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I practice meditation daily,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.03,1:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm wondering what is that process?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.03,1:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that do for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.03,1:16:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does what do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.03,1:16:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.03,1:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.56,1:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the purpose of meditation?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.92,1:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you even do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.63,1:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it because, well, it quiets me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.63,1:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed a little bit of the way I see life, my daily act.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.63,1:16:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly have changed in the way I see other people,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.63,1:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a little less judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.88,1:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's somewhat transformative in its overall effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.88,1:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.88,1:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd have to redefine what your intention is behind the meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.03,1:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you redefine what is the intention of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.03,1:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My intention is to wake up, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.28,1:17:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is to reach the core of truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.28,1:17:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the source, the essence of your own existence?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.28,1:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to see things in their essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.96,1:17:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That should carry you through the next 20, 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.96,1:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.92,1:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, and thanks for coming to Southern California.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.85,1:17:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.85,1:17:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, how important is it to identify mistakes in our past karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.17,1:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and how can we repair those mistakes and errors that we've done to carry us forward?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.72,1:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that happen to you that create suffering,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.86,1:18:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you can dedicate that to the undoing of whatever negative karma you have about that matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.86,1:18:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.67,1:18:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.67,1:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So this morning I banged my knee,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.67,1:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and as for the forgiveness of all the beings whose knees I have hurt,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.10,1:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgave myself for being ignorant and having hurt their knees.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.68,1:18:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I own everything that happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.11,1:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,own everything that happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.11,1:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to process it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.40,1:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Very good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.43,1:18:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know how to stabilize levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.77,1:18:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stabilize what?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.77,1:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.22,1:19:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.23,1:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to tell me what level of consciousness you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.76,1:19:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I experience a number of different levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.76,1:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.96,1:19:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She experienced... You have to talk in the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.81,1:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I experience a number of different levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.81,1:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.81,1:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's like you were saying that you found that the consciousness of the United States had decreased.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.81,1:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.81,1:19:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that it's obvious that one's consciousness can...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.81,1:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,increase and then decrease or, you know, fluctuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.81,1:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.88,1:19:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's normal. It fluctuates.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.88,1:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I would actually...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.88,1:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad, angry, mad, happy, all of them. Half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.88,1:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.88,1:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.88,1:19:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I would like to actually be able to stabilize at...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.88,1:19:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why do you want to stabilize it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.88,1:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say stabilizing in one thing is good?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.88,1:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.88,1:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said that. Did they? No. That's a misconception.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.88,1:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to do is transcend them, move from the lower to the higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.88,1:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not trying to make something stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.97,1:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is process out the negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.97,1:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the positive, you don't have to create.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.97,1:20:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the positive is the inner reality that shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.97,1:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all you want to do is remove the negative by seeing it differently. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.00,1:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the positive, you don't have to try and energize positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.00,1:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the positive automatically takes over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.96,1:20:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When the waves die down on the ocean, the peace prevails.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.18,1:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't create peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.18,1:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go out and create peace on the ocean. You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.25,1:20:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to remove the blocks to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.72,1:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that is how you would recommend...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.72,1:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When you find... When I find that I'm at a lower level of consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.72,1:20:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God, not below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.72,1:20:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, just to identify what it is that's causing the drop in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.72,1:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and then release it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.82,1:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we wrote a book called Transcending Levels of Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.85,1:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one... We tried to address each level to make it sort of clinically specific.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.85,1:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.85,1:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you're stuck with resentment, then you look what's underneath that resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.85,1:21:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you release that, the resentment disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.89,1:21:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like unrealistic expectations.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.89,1:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody should be polite. Everybody should be so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.89,1:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you realize you're being childish, that the world isn't that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.89,1:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you try to relinquish whatever is holding the negative in place.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.89,1:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the negative will then disappear automatically.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.89,1:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't have to try and create the positive or hang on to the positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.14,1:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is remove the blocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.14,1:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove the clouds and the sun shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.14,1:21:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't create the shining of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.31,1:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.81,1:22:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's all you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.47,1:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.64,1:22:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive them even if they're dead wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.10,1:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.43,1:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I'm on the process that you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.52,1:22:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual process.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.52,1:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just been going along.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.68,1:22:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Things come up, I clear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.68,1:22:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been... I experienced peaceful states.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.68,1:22:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced good...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.68,1:22:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You cleared up what?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.68,1:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.68,1:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual process.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.68,1:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He says things come up and he clears them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.68,1:22:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.68,1:22:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.68,1:22:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.68,1:22:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.68,1:22:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I seem to be stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.68,1:22:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to be very, very confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.68,1:22:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I'm completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.68,1:22:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that the spiritual process is very intense now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.68,1:22:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I only think about spiritual things.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.68,1:22:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I read your books constantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.68,1:22:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I play all your tapes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.68,1:22:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I only focus on spiritual things.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.68,1:23:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else seems to matter in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.68,1:23:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And that leads me to a state of confusion of what is...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.47,1:23:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel lost, confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.47,1:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.47,1:23:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this stage, I can't seem to...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.47,1:23:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.47,1:23:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel there's something that's a fear or an anxiety about it that has taken over my
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.57,1:23:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,life, that I'm no longer in control anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.98,1:23:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pray to God to reveal to you what it is you need to clear in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.23,1:23:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.23,1:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask through the Holy Spirit, a miracle, that you become conscious and aware of what specifically
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.06,1:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is the block that you're up against.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.06,1:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.06,1:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been praying to surrender to the will of God, to surrender to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.06,1:23:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and that's sort of a generality, but you're talking more about a specific that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.89,1:23:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're stuck on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.89,1:23:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm more concerned with security, what's going to happen to me, money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.89,1:23:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's probably an issue with that that I...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.89,1:23:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.15,1:23:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.15,1:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're stuck more on one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.15,1:23:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you clear up this one thing and then move to the next?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.15,1:23:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.15,1:23:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.15,1:23:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.15,1:23:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.15,1:23:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.15,1:23:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.15,1:23:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.15,1:24:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.21,1:24:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.21,1:24:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.21,1:24:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.21,1:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.21,1:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.21,1:24:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.40,1:24:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.40,1:24:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.40,1:24:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.40,1:24:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.40,1:24:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.00,1:24:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.00,1:24:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.00,1:24:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.15,1:24:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.15,1:24:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.15,1:24:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.15,1:24:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.15,1:24:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.15,1:24:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,… then move to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.57,1:24:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned specifically money.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.57,1:24:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.57,1:24:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so why don't you work on money?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.02,1:24:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.02,1:24:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry about the other things until you've got that through.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.02,1:24:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Define what works for you about money, whether you see it as a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.02,1:24:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you feel guilty about it, whether you feel deprived.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.02,1:24:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you think there's an insufficiency.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.81,1:24:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Work on money until you can clear that money, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.47,1:24:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And see what money is to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.38,1:24:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is money to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.38,1:24:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.07,1:24:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, security.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.07,1:24:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.42,1:24:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and he got you in for security.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.03,1:24:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I thought it was happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.42,1:24:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's got security.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.35,1:24:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, security brings you happiness, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.60,1:25:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.27,1:25:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that it has to be more linear and logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.94,1:25:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is linear and logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.22,1:25:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Often it's fuzzy and it's a confused field
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.31,1:25:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that you sort of don't know what to do with.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.13,1:25:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.43,1:25:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfectly all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.89,1:25:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to come up like chapters in a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.25,1:25:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now I'll work on those.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.52,1:25:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But things happen that I, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.56,1:25:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I go into states that I don't want, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.31,1:25:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.75,1:25:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.60,1:25:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's normal, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.55,1:25:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So each thing you process as it comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.36,1:25:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive yourself for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.44,1:25:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask to see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.07,1:25:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, most of it is just due to being human.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.60,1:25:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,99.9% is just due to being human.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.76,1:25:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget, humans all have the karma of being human.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.44,1:25:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, oh, Christianity doesn't believe in karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.22,1:25:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.40,1:25:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.77,1:25:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Garden of Eden?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.56,1:25:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're born with negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.43,1:26:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why there's suffering and sin and penance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.31,1:26:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So Christianity believes in plenty of karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.57,1:26:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your penance for?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.88,1:26:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the penance about?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.14,1:26:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're born with original sin.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.05,1:26:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So get away with saying you don't believe in karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.53,1:26:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe in karma plenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.22,1:26:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you get here, you inherit the karma of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.82,1:26:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Disobedience in the Garden of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.36,1:26:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The seduction by the serpent.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.11,1:26:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The serpent seduced the child within the woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.81,1:26:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the adult, the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.56,1:26:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So are we all to feel guilty because some child succumbed to temptation?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.44,1:26:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the infant, the child, the innocence of the child that responded to the serpent.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.10,1:26:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.35,1:27:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So mankind's suffering is because he fell from non-duality into duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.82,1:27:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating of the tree of right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.13,1:27:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.22,1:27:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.64,1:27:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing but duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.77,1:27:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was in the bliss of non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.93,1:27:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And he fell out of that bliss into the complexities and ambivalences and tensions of the linear dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.96,1:27:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't want to hear anything more.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.90,1:27:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no karma in Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.78,1:27:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.75,1:27:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never let it be said again.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.11,1:27:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.65,1:27:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question on studying A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.50,1:27:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.52,1:27:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to feel your energy so that it would help me be a better student.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.19,1:27:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So can I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.52,1:27:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.64,1:27:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.15,1:27:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing the course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.30,1:27:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.80,1:27:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What lesson are you on?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.93,1:27:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on like 58.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.97,1:27:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.68,1:27:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,58.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.22,1:27:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,58.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.85,1:27:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,58.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.81,1:27:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.42,1:27:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up to your ankles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.80,1:28:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.52,1:28:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up to your ankles already.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.77,1:28:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.19,1:28:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.10,1:28:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, I have basically become good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.88,1:28:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at non-attachment and forgiveness, but when I either read fiction or watch movies
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.11,1:28:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which are fiction, I buy into the emotion so intensely that I sometimes can't even sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.69,1:28:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.96,1:28:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.10,1:28:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.53,1:28:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darn.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.42,1:28:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It just brings up whatever's left, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.52,1:28:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sympathy for this, resentment over that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.42,1:28:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.69,1:28:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Identifying the various aspects of the personalities in the movie, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.85,1:28:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So just surrender whatever the movie brings up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.30,1:28:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just keep doing what you're doing with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.15,1:28:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.56,1:29:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you see, television advances, television is a tremendous opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.07,1:29:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows you to live many lifetimes in one, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.22,1:29:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, think how many lifetimes it would take you to live through all the things that you're
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.06,1:29:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,confronted with in just one afternoon of television.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.18,1:29:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In the old days, you could live within two miles of where you were born, spend your
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.93,1:29:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,whole life as a sheepherder, never meet any foreign cultures, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.52,1:29:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why it took many lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.02,1:29:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in the course of an evening, you can be confronted with every complexity and dilemma
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.43,1:29:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the human existence in just one evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.51,1:29:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage and killing and hatred and rivalry and vanity and greed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.35,1:29:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's just intolerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.39,1:29:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty minutes is not even a commercial yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.47,1:29:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So in a way, it speeds up working through.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.77,1:30:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're going to use TV to work through stuff, I think it makes very rapid, because
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.44,1:30:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you keep kind of confronting it all over and over again until finally you let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.10,1:30:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate the bad guys, then you get off that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.96,1:30:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tom Mix used to hate the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.35,1:30:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.92,1:30:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.05,1:30:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.14,1:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.06,1:30:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good and evil in thousands of different formats is what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.39,1:30:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.73,1:30:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.57,1:30:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about calibrating levels of consciousness as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.61,1:30:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been seeing a chiropractor, and she calibrates before and after, and it fluctuates tremendously,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.84,1:30:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.14,1:30:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and I understand that it does do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.77,1:30:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once one goes through the final door, is there still fluctuation?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.96,1:31:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you go through what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.57,1:31:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The final door.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.72,1:31:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The final door.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.52,1:31:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go through the final door, is there still fluctuation?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.92,1:31:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything to be fluctuating, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.75,1:31:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.47,1:31:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.56,1:31:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See, in traditional medicine, they don't believe in kinesiology, they don't believe in chiropractic,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.35,1:31:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't believe in any of those things.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.31,1:31:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I used to use them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.56,1:31:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Used to use them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.61,1:31:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I got through practicing traditionally...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.88,1:31:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I went and saw my chiropractor and got my n***a adjusted.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.85,1:31:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a standing appointment twice a week with my chiropractor, and once a week with my acupuncturist.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.97,1:32:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't tell your regular doctor about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.31,1:32:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to confide in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.68,1:32:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the influence of your work, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.85,1:32:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,First, a gift from a friend of mine that was based on your work that helped me a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.44,1:32:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.86,1:32:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And allow me to read the comments.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.71,1:32:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll read the context of my question first, and then I'll get your answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.76,1:32:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my observation that in most of the ancient traditional forms of spiritual practices,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.64,1:32:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,which I've investigated and applied in my own life,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.84,1:32:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,physical health practices were emphasized by the devotee to prepare the body to handle the energy of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.69,1:32:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems to me that many advanced spiritual teachers have experienced various illnesses, pain, injuries,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.81,1:32:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and their progressives.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.02,1:32:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to ask Dr. Hawkins to tell us a little bit more about that, and then I'm going to ask Dr. Hawkins to tell us a little bit more about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.97,1:33:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, how important is it for a spiritual aspirant to practice applying principles of health,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.93,1:33:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,such as nutrition and physical exercise, in addition to spiritual practice, to speed one's realization of truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.73,1:33:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And do these practices make the transfiguration process easier or faster?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.56,1:33:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.17,1:33:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.90,1:33:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good for their own sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.47,1:33:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good because you're giving recognition, you know, to the blessing of life itself, affirming its value.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.28,1:33:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it help you advance your level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.18,1:33:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.13,1:33:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then can I have one more question on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.46,1:33:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If that, and I'm going to say if that was so, but of course it is, you just said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.68,1:33:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a valuable...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.06,1:33:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The teaching of physical health...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.61,1:34:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The teaching of physical health practices, because it's kind of endeared to my own heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.46,1:34:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is that a valuable form of service for me to improve the quality of people's lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.10,1:34:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the quality.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.46,1:34:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the quality of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.61,1:34:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's respect for the gift of life, to maintain it in as best a condition as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.03,1:34:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.38,1:34:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's recognition of the gift, affirmation of the gift, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.48,1:34:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For a certain level, that would be meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.43,1:34:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.85,1:34:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Another meaning level, it would be...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.30,1:34:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be non-meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.55,1:34:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you leave this planet, you don't leave in the best health, usually.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.64,1:34:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You died in fit condition, with 32 push-ups and stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.77,1:35:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way to go, in good shape.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.77,1:35:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be in good shape when I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.39,1:35:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.43,1:35:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It increases one's joie de vivre.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.31,1:35:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.94,1:35:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good physical health.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.80,1:35:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy of life is you ought to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.57,1:35:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate the joy of your own existence exuberantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.43,1:35:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.11,1:35:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you, first of all, for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.97,1:35:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, how do you actually surrender the juice?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.47,1:35:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a better process?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.15,1:35:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there one process that is better than the other one?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.80,1:35:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get one?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.76,1:35:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you surrender the juice?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.93,1:35:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there one process better than another?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.18,1:35:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.19,1:35:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.56,1:35:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion to God, the willingness...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.50,1:35:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of your love for God, you're willing to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.85,1:35:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect pleasures of juicing negativity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.48,1:36:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For thee, O Lord, I'm willing to give up the glee of hating the SOB, even though he deserves it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.56,1:36:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see the absurdity of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.84,1:36:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you laugh at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.15,1:36:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you ask God for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.89,1:36:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you be so ignorant?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.42,1:36:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.93,1:36:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.05,1:36:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's audible.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.86,1:36:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out of love that you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.10,1:36:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out of love for God that this stands in the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.10,1:36:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it stands in the way between that and that which you love and strive for,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.72,1:36:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're willing to relinquish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.92,1:36:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to remind yourself, you're relinquishing the lesser for the greater.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.65,1:36:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's very fun to hate somebody and stab them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.96,1:36:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.42,1:36:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that is fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.89,1:37:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that, you SOB.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.38,1:37:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, especially when you're doing it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.93,1:37:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, the willingness to let it go is sort of done on the basis of faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.52,1:37:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That as enjoyable as that is, that there is something greater.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.23,1:37:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you take the word of the teacher, that something greater will take its place.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.02,1:37:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a certain amount of faith and trust in the teacher that letting go of that will create the space for the greater.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.53,1:37:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's letting go of the lesser for the greater.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.06,1:37:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on confidence in the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.88,1:37:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one thing a teacher in body can provide is certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.06,1:37:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your intuition tells you whether he's telling you the truth or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.93,1:37:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And if letting it go, you're going to be more miserable, he wouldn't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.77,1:37:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, no, if you give up rage, revenge, hatred, and guilt, you will come to a more joyful state.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.18,1:38:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you will be doing good to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.05,1:38:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because of what you...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.52,1:38:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because of what you do, but because of what you have become, that your life then becomes a blessing to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.71,1:38:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That you exist is already uplifting the rest of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.21,1:38:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's the gift that you give, by letting it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.18,1:38:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.68,1:38:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's St. Francis of Assisi's prayer, that I may be a channel of thy will, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.46,1:38:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.96,1:38:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.46,1:38:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say, first of all, that it's a blessing just to be in your presence, and I appreciate the time that you're giving us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.64,1:38:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am absolutely freezing, and you're warm, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.57,1:38:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.46,1:38:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's warm-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.06,1:38:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, well, first of all, the statement is that a few years ago, while I was reading one of your books, it was either eye or eye of the eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.75,1:39:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something spontaneously happened where all of a sudden I had this visual of this entire life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.89,1:39:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was localized to this lifetime, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.64,1:39:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The visual narration, if you would, was every event that's happened to me that was important, and some that at the time seemed trivial, but now it was clear that they were incredibly important.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.64,1:39:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only these events, but the sequence of these events made complete sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.76,1:39:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was absolutely clear from the earliest memory up until the time where I was holding your book.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.76,1:39:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just wondering if you could provide me any insight into, first of all, what it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.11,1:39:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, why do I only remember the general theme of it and its meaning, and not the minutiae that I was going through?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.14,1:39:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what would you want to remember the minutiae for?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.92,1:40:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it gave such beauty to every event that spontaneously arose in my vision.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.97,1:40:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the process isn't that. It was just that real.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.31,1:40:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was the event that happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.25,1:40:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about a whole sequence of events. What do you mean, that event?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.25,1:40:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have lasted. I couldn't tell you. It was almost like it was outside of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.25,1:40:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been five seconds. It could have been a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.25,1:40:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was outside of time. It's death's door. Life unreels before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.35,1:40:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're familiar with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.35,1:40:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.35,1:40:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you might have been there. Death's door.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.35,1:40:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.03,1:41:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can put your life on a videotape, and then you can run it fast or slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.89,1:41:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.86,1:41:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing a spiritual technique since I was a teenager, and I enjoyed doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.96,1:41:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some nice experiences. I've grown from it, which I can attribute to some after effects of the technique,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.96,1:41:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or I can attribute it just to growing older and life experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.31,1:41:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After reading in one of your books about the deepest level of reality being infinite love,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.80,1:41:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it reminded me of a verse from the Bible, which goes,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.63,1:41:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He who abides in love abides in God, and God in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.63,1:41:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, since infinite love is at our deepest essence,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.46,1:41:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a way to invoke that love as a way of enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.13,1:42:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, which I just said before to the last person.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.89,1:42:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you don't try to invoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.85,1:42:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite love, what you do is you constantly remove the blocks that stand in the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.85,1:42:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot force the sun to shine brighter than it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.85,1:42:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can do is remove the clouds, and as you remove the clouds, the sun shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.85,1:42:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it's not in control. It's not a linear, I do this, now this will happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.85,1:42:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more a generality that you keep chipping away at all the negativity.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.02,1:42:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.02,1:42:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When least expected, when least expected, suddenly it opens up before you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.07,1:42:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.64,1:42:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't because you're doing this practice, this happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.64,1:42:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work in a causal, it's not in a causal sequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.56,1:43:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't align yourself with love.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.56,1:43:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more that by commitment, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.56,1:43:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.56,1:43:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a becomingness, and that which one becomes, then how it has the power
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.56,1:43:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to summon forth certain phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.56,1:43:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So by aligning...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.56,1:43:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're listening to what I'm saying instead of talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.56,1:43:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.56,1:43:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you constantly let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.05,1:43:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop putting it in a linear, I do this, that causes this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.23,1:43:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I be doing to cause that?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.23,1:43:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.23,1:43:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.65,1:43:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep removing the negativity itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.65,1:43:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I said, as you remove the clouds, the sun shines forth of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.78,1:43:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because you removed the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.94,1:43:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you're holding it is, if I remove the clouds, then the sun's going to shine
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.94,1:43:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.94,1:43:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's looking at it in a linear causality framework again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.94,1:43:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.10,1:43:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to cause anything or bring on any kind of state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.72,1:43:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remove that which you observe to be negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.72,1:43:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.72,1:44:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.88,1:44:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to take...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.88,1:44:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.88,1:44:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to take a ten minute break or so?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.88,1:44:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.88,1:44:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many people I can see in the back of the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.28,1:44:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you do, you have...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.28,1:44:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a break from right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.28,1:44:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.28,1:44:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to talk to the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.28,1:44:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.35,1:44:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.35,1:44:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.35,1:44:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.35,1:44:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.35,1:44:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.35,1:44:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Be diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.35,1:44:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.35,1:44:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to work on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.80,1:44:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the amount of people that have questions, we have to be out of here at 5
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.80,1:44:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,o'clock, so we're going to go ahead and answer questions through the next break.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.80,1:44:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just to let you know, we will not be taking an afternoon break.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.80,1:44:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to continue with questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.80,1:44:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bookshop.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.80,1:44:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bookshop will be closing shortly, so this will be your last opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.80,1:45:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another event after us, so we'll probably have to be out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.30,1:45:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tremendous gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.30,1:45:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of you a couple of weeks ago because I was outside and I saw a beetle on the ground
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.48,1:45:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on its back flipped over with its nose in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.48,1:45:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went and promptly bent down and nudged it back over on its front.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.48,1:45:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But he looks up and says to me, hey, I'll pretend to die here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.48,1:45:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he immediately flips back around.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.48,1:45:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Put his legs back up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.48,1:45:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was going to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.48,1:45:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He interrupted his funeral.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.48,1:45:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.48,1:45:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll just let him keep going there.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.48,1:45:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.48,1:45:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout this lifetime, I've had pretty extreme allergies.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.48,1:45:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And mentally, I know that allergies are an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.72,1:45:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And spiritually, I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.72,1:45:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender and I don't resist them and but physically I'm a train wreck you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.72,1:46:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,know and so my question about suffering about what you brought up earlier about
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.10,1:46:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how suffering can be a form of devotion and although the time that seemed
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.40,1:46:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,decided really beautiful I also a red flag went up and I thought wow that's a
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.78,1:46:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,way my ego is going to say see sufferings I can suffer and be devoted
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.85,1:46:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for whatever and so I just wanted to see if you could elaborate on the clear
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.01,1:46:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,differences about the kind of suffering that I might go through with allergies
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.48,1:46:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,or and how I might be contextualize that into a form of devotion well you have to
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.23,1:46:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,let go you're an infinite being you're only subject to what you hold in mind so
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.25,1:46:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,pollen doesn't have any power over you
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.59,1:46:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only your belief in the power of pollen so the pollen itself has no power
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.40,1:47:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if we calibrate pollen, pollen calibrates over 90 it has very little power
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.05,1:47:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're over 90 so it's your belief you see people are upset when I say you
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.98,1:47:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,know certain things global warming human activity has nothing to do with global warming
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.65,1:47:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,oh they just go off and do a fit doesn't have anything to do with it has to do with
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.85,1:47:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,magnetism
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.47,1:47:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,magnetic activity the surface of the Sun you calibrate that that comes out
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.13,1:47:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,through all of mankind raises the temperature on the planet earth about
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.18,1:47:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,point zero point eight degrees max all the self-sacrificing and stuff is
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.84,1:47:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing magnetic activity the surface of the Sun so when they go do polar polar
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.85,1:47:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,borings down to 10,000 years ago temperature depends on the surface
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.56,1:47:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,activity of the Sun that makes people very upset when you say that
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.30,1:48:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they got a vested interest in the whole belief system see yeah I've been aware
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.52,1:48:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that the pollen is that it's not really can it really affect me negatively I
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.18,1:48:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,think it's very early age it's transitory yeah it's transitory it's
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.43,1:48:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,transitory you know you grow out of it maybe 20 30 minutes now in it to being
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.42,1:48:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only subject to what I'm holding in mind and pollen is neutral it has no
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.89,1:48:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's either good in the good or bad and it tends to run in families you get to
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.53,1:48:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,other people in your family not that I never aware of you're the only one as
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.10,1:48:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,far as I know that's unusual yes you see the whole bunch but there you can
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.46,1:48:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend it you can transcend that thank you I transcended that poison
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.89,1:48:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you know a bunch of other things
